Name: Location
Description: Documents the location of the data file as a description. Supports the multi-language content.

Name: DataFileURI
Description: A URN or URL for the data file with a flag to indicate if it is a public copy.

Name: SizeInBytes
Description: Specifies the size of the file in bytes.

Name: IsMaster
Description: Set to "true" when this file is the master file (in the case that there are multiple, i.e. backup, copies).
